Mysql-Database Instrument

To finish the installation and use this instrument you have one more step:

  1) Setup Your database connection file example:
  
      $db['development'] = array(
      	'type' 			=> 'mysql',
      	'server'		=> 'localhost',
      	'user'			=> 'root',
      	'password'	=> 'root',
      	'name'			=> 'orchestra_development'
      );

      $db['test'] = array(
      	'type' 			=> 'mysql',
      	'server'		=> 'localhost',
      	'user'			=> 'root',
      	'password'	=> 'root',
      	'name'			=> 'orchestra_test'
      );

      $db['production'] = array(
      	'type' 			=> 'mysql',
      	'server'		=> 'localhost',
      	'user'			=> 'root',
      	'password'	=> 'root',
      	'name'			=> 'orchestra_production'
      );
      
      
Enjoy!

